asset.hookText:
Calling all OXO fans! Do you think you have what it takes to be called the Worlds Biggest OXOniac?

OXO is developing a series of How-To videos to play on the web and were looking for our biggest fans to star in them. If you think youve got what it takes, create a 30  90 second audition video to show off your demo skills. Were looking for fans that are comfortable in the kitchen, cool in front of the camera and can clearly demonstrate their favorite product.

3 Grand Prize Winners will receive a starring role in OXOs How-To Videos.
